{"tid":1001190,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦再簽「美斯」 1.7億購土耳其美斯","createTime":"2019-01-30T03:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T19:43:54.000Z","uid":54373,"like":68,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfd7f3d008f040abded20be67d8e093b30788a7","tid":1001190,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒報道，利物浦早前相中效力土超特拉布宗的19歲新星、被外界譽為「土耳其美斯」的奧梅爾（Abdulkadir Omur），最新消息指出，紅軍已經與特拉布宗達成轉會協議，將會2,000萬歐元（約1.7億港元）的價格收購此子，並會於今夏正式來投。<br />\n<br />\n現年只得19歲的奧梅爾，是特拉布宗青訓產品，三年前已為該隊首次上陣，去季更穩坐正選上陣29場攻入3球，更一直是土耳其青年軍成員，身高只得1米68的他可勝任兩翼及進攻中場位置，被視為「土耳其美斯」。假若這宗轉會最終順利完成，將是紅軍繼簽入祖高美斯、「埃及美斯」穆罕默德沙拿及「瑞士美斯」梳頓沙基利，又一位「美斯」來投。"},{"pid":"48bd41149b6f7d45baf12762db9287e0920a7a2a","tid":1001190,"uid":13480,"like":271,"dislike":1,"score":270,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"29場入3球都美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1cab7780c0b10dd925e1fbc46985f31e0b2272","tid":1001190,"uid":46042,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"美斯首奪英超冠軍"},{"pid":"1972459a330da88a4558533162bfeb1ba929c16c","tid":1001190,"uid":52571,"like":87,"dislike":4,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:13:58.000Z","msg":"有個爾字既球員十成都伏黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07eface0edd1c7c92c7e022bcf1fd9869bab9cf","tid":1001190,"uid":39012,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"終於出現美斯地球聯合軍"},{"pid":"291f385d999f1b58c14b507a76e37d2ed2eee03d","tid":1001190,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"108cdd929ab0374870284947e74a7e18f28615c2","tid":1001190,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"邊個係香港美斯？"},{"pid":"75520ba776921b210b9caae83e957a150be4d4e7","tid":1001190,